HEADWORD: Fencer
<hw>Fen"cer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who fences; one
who teaches or practices the art of fencing with sword or
foil.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>As blunt as the <qex>fencer's</qex> foils.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fencible</ent>⟦br⟧
